- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach to improve the training of GANs, which is a popular topic in the field of artificial intelligence. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper utilizes neural networks as the core component of the proposed framework, which falls under the scope of neural and evolutionary computing. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The paper focuses on generating images, which is a common task in computer graphics.
